'''Xylen''' was a substance which [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[Xylen chip|computer chips]] had been made out of. Its use was apparently ended by [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]]. Xylen was a very valuable material and half a crate of xylen chips was worth 750.000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] by then.

